\c 49 
\pc \bd 49\bd*

\s Ee Baba, nitakuwa kama Yesu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ee Baba, nitakuwa kama Yesu, Baraka ile alinipatia\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Ni mushangao na ajabu pia, Kwa sura yake atanigeuza.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ee Bwana Yesu, nani kama wewe Alinipenda hata nitazameMilele utukufu wako, Kristo, Mimi zawabu ya mateso yako\bd*\bd ?\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Mapendo yako hayakustarehe Mbele ya kubariki wana wako\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Yanashiriki vitu vyote nasi, Hata uriti wako, Bwana Yesu,\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Wapenzi wako wote kwa milele Kwa utukufu watakusanyika, Na kwa furaha watakuzunguka, Kukuabudu na kukutukuza.\bd*
